    SP5QWB for reporting.

 -- Joop Stakenborg <pa3aba@debian.org>  Sun, 17 Nov 2002 21:15:11 +0100

xdx (0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed a scrolling bug for the text widget.
  * Set the g_io_channel encoding to binary to support the many different
    languages used on the cluster, utf8 encoding would cause iconv failures
    on receiving a message, which lead to disconnects.
  * Some work on the about box.
  * The statusbar is cleared after 30 seconds.
  * French translations by Jean-Luc Coulon <jean-luc.coulon at wanadoo.fr>.
  * Provide rpm packages.
  * Fixed some memory leaks with memprof.
  * Some code rewrites.
  * Debian: do not create symlinks to /usr/doc (lintian).

 -- Joop Stakenborg <pa3aba@debian.org>  Fri, 30 Aug 2002 13:28:00 +0200

xdx (0.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * First public release. 

